6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to agriculture; designating the
Oklahoma Department of Agriculture, Food, and
8 Forestry as the state educational agency referenced
by the National School Lunch Act; providing that the
9 Oklahoma Department of Agriculture, Food, and
Forestry may secure and administer the benefits of
10 the National School Lunch Act; directing the Oklahoma
Department of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry to
11 provide general supervision of the school lunch
program; creating the School Lunch Workshop Revolving
12 Fund; providing for the allocation of funds for the
school lunch program; amending 70 O.S. 2021, Section
13 3-104, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 445,
O.S.L. 2024 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 3-104),
14 which relates to the State Board of Education's
powers and duties; removing the State Board of
15 Education from overseeing and administering school
lunch program under the National School Lunch Act;
16 repealing 70 O.S. 2021, Section 3-119, which relates
to the school lunch program; providing for
17 codification; and providing an effective date.
18
